{"tid":493063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過馬路要小心！警方今起嚴捉亂過馬路","createTime":"2017-12-08T07:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T07:09:48.000Z","uid":10958,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"99e7fde74dee3853d68b30dbf9c76cd607d2b1fa","tid":493063,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:09:48.000Z","msg":"<strong>過馬路要小心！警方今起嚴捉亂過馬路</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201612/20161208182322_2_cross.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201612%2F20161208182322_2_cross.jpg&h=678ca79a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提提大家，近日過馬路要小心！警務處公布將於12月8日起至12日期間進行全港行人道路安全行動，警方將執法票控亂過馬路的行人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201612/20161208182322_3_cross2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201612%2F20161208182322_3_cross2.jpg&h=5d7d4dac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行動期間，警方將進行執法，票控亂過馬路或干犯嚴重違例事項的行人。不單衝紅燈，於距離行人過路設施十五米範圍內而不使用該些設施橫過馬路，及攀越路邊圍欄或穿過中央分道帶進入車路等均屬交通罪行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201612/20161208182322_2_cross.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201612%2F20161208182322_2_cross.jpg&h=678ca79a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家記得做個守法公民，睇清楚先過馬路！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/202269/%E9%81%8E%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF%E8%A6%81%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E4%BB%8A%E8%B5%B7%E5%9A%B4%E6%8D%89%E4%BA%82%E9%81%8E%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F202269%2F%25E9%2581%258E%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25BB%258A%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%259A%25B4%25E6%258D%2589%25E4%25BA%2582%25E9%2581%258E%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25B7%25AF%2F1&d=UYGkvbzWySGVpgnXueqqfBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=bf1738ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/202269/%E9%81%8E%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF%E8%A6%81%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E4%BB%8A%E8%B5%B7%E5%9A%B4%E6%8D%89%E4%BA%82%E9%81%8E%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF/1</a><br />\n來源：政府新聞網<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.news.gov.hk/tc/categories/law_order/html/2017/02/20170203_164316.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcategories%2Flaw_order%2Fhtml%2F2017%2F02%2F20170203_164316.shtml&d=UYGkvbzWySGVpgnXueqqfBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=35820593\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.news.gov.hk/tc/categories/law_order/html/2017/02/20170203_164316.shtml</a>"}]}